info: Rating, 5 stars,  · August 2023,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment:
The apartment is located close to shops, restaurants, and easy access to and from Uttara. The building is very clean and safe. The aircons, water heater, and washing machine, work as needed. The kithcen is large and has almost everything to prepare and eat food at the apartment.
The owner is very prompt in looking into any issues and has a responsible team. Recommend this place for people looking to stay in a nice area in Uttara.
